# LensTemper Advisory Adapter

LensTemper is available in this repository as a portable skill package. Cursor
support is conditional full only when the run satisfies `docs/hosts/cursor.md`;
otherwise it is advisory/reference.

Use this rule only when the user asks for LensTemper, a LensTemper-style review,
or an advisory plan/spec review through Cursor.

Required references:

- `docs/hosts/cursor.md`
- `reviews/README.md`
- `reviews/registry.json`
- selected lens prompts under `reviews/lenses/`
- selected lens manifests under `reviews/manifests/lenses/`
- `reviews/reviewer-template.md`

Cursor-only output must be labeled advisory/reference unless the run uses a
detached orchestrator, fresh per-lens reviewers, per-lens JSON artifacts,
`ledger.json`, `events.jsonl`, synthesis, rerun decisions,
`completion-summary.json`, validators, and a parent-chat-only isolation scan.
